    {
      "id": "08eb8783-726c-4fb0-8f29-968c3bbf4aea",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Work focuses on short-courses with a single outcome at the end meaning that the courses only have a final evaluation at the end and no intermediate assessments. To address the lack of data, authors rely on Social Network Analysis to obtain new features.",
